    <item>
      <title>里夫斯称，私募股权经理冒着自有资本的风险将避免劳工税上调</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-18/private-equity-managers-risking-capital-to-avoid-labour-tax-hike</link>
      <description><![CDATA[雷切尔·里夫斯 (Rachel Reeves) 表示，私募股权经理以自有资本承担风险所获得的附带权益将不受工党提高私募股权基金经理税收计划的影响。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-18/private-equity-managers-risking-capital-to-avoid-labour-tax-hike</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 18 Jun 2024 07:06:41 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>勒庞领导的政党称需要绝对多数才能执掌法国大选</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-18/le-pen-s-party-says-it-needs-absolute-majority-to-govern-france</link>
      <description><![CDATA[国民联盟领导人乔丹·巴德拉呼吁支持者帮助他的政党及其盟友在法国的提前选举中取得压倒性胜利，以便他能够执政，为极右翼掌握政策制定权设定了高标准。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-18/le-pen-s-party-says-it-needs-absolute-majority-to-govern-france</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 18 Jun 2024 06:38:30 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>李克强访马前，安瓦尔称马来西亚正计划加入金砖国家</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-18/malaysia-is-planning-to-join-brics-anwar-says-ahead-of-li-visit</link>
      <description><![CDATA[马来西亚总理安瓦尔·易卜拉欣表示，这个东南亚国家将加入金砖国家经济集团，成为该不断扩大的组织中的最新一个国家，该组织被视为对西方主导的全球秩序构成挑战。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-18/malaysia-is-planning-to-join-brics-anwar-says-ahead-of-li-visit</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 18 Jun 2024 06:28:18 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>西藏流亡政府称美国法律迫使中国谈判</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-18/us-law-on-tibet-puts-pressure-on-china-for-talks-official-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[西藏政府一名官员表示，美国出台的新西藏法以及美国议员对西藏的高调访问将给中国带来压力，迫使其与西藏流亡政府接触。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-18/us-law-on-tibet-puts-pressure-on-china-for-talks-official-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 18 Jun 2024 05:48:48 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>普里扬卡·甘地将在印度补选中首次亮相</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-18/priyanka-gandhi-vadra-to-make-electoral-debut-to-retain-key-india-seat</link>
      <description><![CDATA[印度尼赫鲁-甘地政治王朝的后代普里扬卡·甘地·瓦德拉 (Priyanka Gandhi Vadra) 将在其兄长、反对党印度国民大会党高层领导人拉胡尔·甘地 (Rahul Gandhi) 最近赢得的选区首次参加选举。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-18/priyanka-gandhi-vadra-to-make-electoral-debut-to-retain-key-india-seat</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 18 Jun 2024 05:04:08 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国官员的言论被爆红 为澳大利亚之行蒙上阴影</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-18/china-s-cheng-lei-gaffe-overshadows-premier-li-qiang-s-australia-visit</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国官员阻拦记者、曾被拘留的成蕾的行为，有可能给李强总理访问澳大利亚带来影响，澳大利亚总理安东尼·阿尔巴尼斯 (Anthony Albanese) 表示，他对此行为感到担忧。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-18/china-s-cheng-lei-gaffe-overshadows-premier-li-qiang-s-australia-visit</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 18 Jun 2024 03:19:12 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>李强访问珀斯 中澳矿产紧张局势备受关注</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-18/china-australia-critical-mineral-tensions-in-spotlight-as-li-qiang-visits-perth</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在李强总理访问的最后一天，北京和堪培拉之间在中国对澳大利亚关键矿产行业投资问题上的分歧成为了焦点。李强总理与澳大利亚总理安东尼·阿尔巴尼斯在西部矿业之都珀斯会面。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-18/china-australia-critical-mineral-tensions-in-spotlight-as-li-qiang-visits-perth</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 18 Jun 2024 00:42:56 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>危机加深 他信、泰国总理陷入法律诉讼</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-17/thaksin-set-for-indictment-as-court-weighs-thai-premier-s-future</link>
      <description><![CDATA[泰国前领导人他信·西那瓦因侮辱王室一案面临审判，而最高法院命令他的盟友兼总理斯雷塔·达维辛提交更多证据以要求罢免他，这一举动加剧了这个东南亚国家的政治危机。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-17/thaksin-set-for-indictment-as-court-weighs-thai-premier-s-future</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 17 Jun 2024 21:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>马克龙的困境令欧洲担忧国防和乌克兰问题</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-17/macron-s-struggles-have-europe-fretting-over-defense-and-ukraine</link>
      <description><![CDATA[法国的政治动荡引起一些欧盟国家政府的担忧，他们担心联合军费开支和新一轮支持乌克兰的举措可能会被搁置。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-17/macron-s-struggles-have-europe-fretting-over-defense-and-ukraine</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 17 Jun 2024 18:21:11 GMT</pubDate>
